title: Marat Garayev
text:
Marat Rinatovich Garayev (; born 20 May 1990) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He played 3 seasons in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20KAMAZ%20Naberezhnye%20Chelny">FC KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny</a>.
